<p class="body">For CMOs at financial technology starting their AI deployment, the highest-ROI starting stack is:</p>
<ul class="ul">
<li><strong>Claude Team ($30/seat)</strong> as the foundation for reasoning and writing</li>
<li><strong>Industry-appropriate vertical tool</strong> (varies — see industry-specific guide)</li>
<li><strong>Meeting summary tool</strong> (Fathom, Otter, or Gong if revenue-team)</li>
<li><strong>Lead/customer intelligence tool</strong> appropriate for your motion</li>
</ul>
<p class="body">Total starting investment: $500-$2,000/month depending on team size. ROI usually positive within 90 days.</p>
</div></section>

